Class NestedSelectorScopedLocatorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.qa.bb.scope.nestedselector.NestedSelectorScopedLocatorFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParentElementLocatorProvider, org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocatorFactory

    public class NestedSelectorScopedLocatorFactory
extends Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocatorFactory, ParentElementLocatorProvider
    Locator factory that scopes given searchContext using a By selector. Reduces search scope by using parent scope
